      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just hard to see the point of any of this sometimes. like, if you look at the physics of it... the universe is just gonna end in heat death anyway. trillions of years of nothingness. so what is the actual point of struggling, or building anything, or even just being? it all feels like a massive, cosmic joke.",
